Changes to apply to /etc/nixos/configuration.nix:

1. i3 extraPackages — add rofi, remove polybar:

    windowManager.i3 = {
      enable = true;
      configFile = "/etc/i3.conf";
      extraPackages = with pkgs; [
        dmenu
        rofi
        xorg.xrandr
        i3lock
        i3blocks
     ];
    };

2. Remove polybar stub config (delete lines 202-210):

  DELETE:
  environment.etc."config/polybar" = {
    text = ''
      [bar/example]
      width = 100%
      height = 27
      radius = 6.0
      fixed-center = false
    '';
  };

3. Enable xss-lock for suspend/idle protection (replace commented block at lines 433-439):

  programs.xss-lock = {
    enable = true;
    lockerCommand = "${pkgs.i3lock}/bin/i3lock -c 282828";
  };

4. Remove dunst from systemPackages (home-manager now manages it):

  environment.systemPackages = with pkgs; [
    acpi
    iw
    lm_sensors

    git
    htop

    libnotify

    pavucontrol

    cifs-utils

    libnvidia-container
    nvidia-container-toolkit
    nvidia-container-toolkit.tools
    runc

    cachix
  ];

5. Remove I3CONFIG_DMENU_INCLUDE (rofi doesn't need a whitelist filter):

  environment.extraInit = ''
  export I3CONFIG_DEFAULT_TERMINAL="alacritty"
  '';
